title: KAMANDI part 2
description:
Ladies and Gentlemen, here it is. By request from the forums and elsewhere:

The remaining Kamandi books that were not included in my first torrent.

This includes Kamandi issues 41-59 and the unpublished pages from 60 and 61 and the 6 issue Elseworlds mini series from 1993.

The later issues of Kamandi included an OMAC back-up feature by Jim Starlin.


I have also included Kamandi appearances:
Karate Kid 15, Brave and the Bold 120 and 157 and DCCP 64.

Thanks to the scanners and all of you who contributed to putting this torrent together from the forums and the SIR.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
